eReport` and `RevisionTargets` provide useful structured data for debugging and future enhancements.\n\n## Issues Found\n- None.\n\n## Verdict: PASS\n\n## Notes for Lead Agent\n- The hardening item regarding `bootstrap_identity` was confirmed to be addressed in `cypherclaw_daemon.py` and `daemon.py`.\n- All 56 critique tests (31 new + 25 existing) passed successfully.\n","file_path":"sdp/verification/t-023@20260416t054258z-verify.md"}}
